    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2020-03-25</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2020-04-24T18:35:05Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Emergency Community Supervision Act</b></p> <p>This bill establishes measures to reduce the number of individuals in federal custody during a national emergency relating to a communicable disease.</p> <p>Specifically, it does the following:</p> <ul> <li>requires certain categories of inmates to be released and placed in community supervision (e.g., home confinement); </li> <li>limits the use of pretrial detention; and </li> <li>modifies supervised release, including to limit the use of incarceration as a sanction for a parole violation. </li> </ul>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
